            "descriptionRaw": "<color=#FFD780FF>Normal Attack</color>\nThrows things that go boom when they hit things! Performs up to 3 explosive attacks, dealing <color=#FF9999FF>AoE Pyro DMG</color>.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Charged Attack</color>\nConsumes a certain amount of Stamina and deals <color=#FF9999FF>AoE Pyro DMG</color> to opponents after a short casting time.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Plunging Attack</color>\nGathering the power of Pyro, Klee plunges towards the ground from mid-air, damaging all opponents in her path. Deals <color=#FF9999FF>AoE Pyro DMG</color> upon impact with the ground.",
            "name": "Kaboom!"
        },
