            "descriptionRaw": "Jumpy Dumpty is tons of boom-bang-fun! \nWhen thrown, Jumpy Dumpty bounces thrice, igniting and dealing <color=#FF9999FF>AoE Pyro DMG</color> with every bounce.\n\nOn the third bounce, the bomb splits into many mines.\nThe mines will explode upon contact with opponents, or after a short period of time, dealing <color=#FF9999FF>AoE Pyro DMG</color>.\n\nStarts with 2 charges.\n\n<i>Jumpy Dumpty is Klee's good friend! She can't help but introduce him to everyone.</i>",
            "name": "Jumpy Dumpty"
        },
