            "descriptionRaw": "Klee's Blazing Delight! For the duration of this ability, continuously summons Sparks 'n' Splash to attack nearby opponents, dealing <color=#FF9999FF>AoE Pyro DMG</color>.\n\n<i>The knights all believe that Klee must have a lucky star watching over her to have never been hurt by any of her own bombs...</i>",
